<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois.cgi?Spiro">Spiro</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 10:29 p.m. 16/6/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: Paladin RP<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/forum/prexus.cgi?read=21" TARGET=_self>Paladin RP</A> (Vesentac)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>I'm sorry, but as a Paladin, regardless of lovey dove you god is, you have a responsibility to remove the evil desicration of such races as dark elves, and orcs, and the likes of all of them. That's why those classes can't be paladins. Paladins good, good kills evil, it's how it works.

<BR>No matter how well you can justify yourself, RP, that grouping was totally out of the question. If nothing else, the Dark elf shouldn't have agreed to group with you, seeing as how that would be totally agains his nature.
<P>On a side note, how can you justify making a complaint such as this, when you started off the message with, I was "TANKING" with a dark elf enchanter. It just seems a contradiction of terms to me, RP and Tanking.
<P>If you have anything else to say on the subject, feel free to flame me, I will always respond and mine will always be more rational, and be a better arguement. I'm not saying this to brag, I'm saying as a point of fact, and a warning for if you choose to proceed. Oh, and please don't quible on technicalities or spelling errors if you do get into a heated arguement with me, that's just childish.
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
